      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a practical choice for someone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor paint fading on the hood, and a few small dings. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and wear, though the cabin remains functional. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it may require some minor maintenance soon to address a slightly noisy suspension and aging tires. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the frills.",
