    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, boasting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering the discerning driver a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising quality. We invite serious inquiries for this investment-grade acquisition.",
