      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute gem of a car. Seriously, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership hassle, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
