    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise ZF 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically peerless, it has undergone proactive dual-VANOS timing adjustment and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, offering telepathic steering feedback. With flawless paint depth and a pristine underside, this is a turn-key example for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection and chassis integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
