      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear, and the original floor mats are spotless. Every electronic component, from the advanced infotainment system to the climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history from the authorized dealership and a recently completed major inspection. It sits on a set of premium tires with near-full tread. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Clean title in hand, single-owner history, and a strictly smoke-free environment.",
